                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-65-victim693 t18130714-65-viclabel386"></join> woman: I live at No. 5, <placeName id="t18130714-65-crimeloc387">Steward's-rents, Drury-lane</placeName>
